COMMENT ON COLUMN forest_cover_geometry.feature_class_skey IS E'Unique identifier of the feature class.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forest_cover_geometry.feature_perimeter IS E'The perimeter of the polygon pertaining to the Forest Cover measured in metres.';
