COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.forhealth_rslt_id IS E'System generated value uniquely identifying the forest health damage agent occurrance.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.incidence_area IS E'The area in hectares of the region involved.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.incidence_pct IS E'The percentage of the Standards Unit or Opening that the agent is affecting as defined by the survey strata.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.observation_date IS E'The date this observation was made.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.opening_id IS E'System generated value uniquely identifying the opening.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.revision_count IS E'Internal counter used by the system to avoid conflicting updates to the record.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.silv_damage_agent_code IS E'A code indicating the category of insect or disease that has caused a disturbance in the stands history. Stands with a disturbance caused by insects or disease can be further described by the ACTIVITY SUB CODE. The code for the damage agent as it is currently collected (94-3). The FIP based version of Damage Agent code, retained on an as is basis until migration to a stable Ministry version of Damage Agent is availible.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.update_timestamp IS E'The date and time of the last update.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN forhealth_rslt.update_userid IS E'The USERID of the individual who last updated the information.';


