COMMENT ON COLUMN stocking_standard_unit.net_area IS E'A value in hectares for the net area to be reforested (NAR). The NAR is the total area under the prescription (TAUP) minus the area or no planned reforestation (NPR).';
COMMENT ON COLUMN stocking_standard_unit.opening_id IS E'System generated value uniquely identifying the opening.';
