COMMENT ON COLUMN stocking_standard_unit.standards_regime_id IS E'Unique identifier for the STANDARD REGIME entry.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN stocking_standard_unit.standards_unit_id IS E'A unique identifier within the opening that identifies the standard unit. At least one standards unit per opening is required.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN stocking_standard_unit.stocking_standard_unit_id IS E'System generated value uniquely identifing the stocking standards.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN stocking_standard_unit.update_timestamp IS E'The date and time of the last update.';
COMMENT ON COLUMN stocking_standard_unit.update_userid IS E'The USERID of the individual who last updated the information.';
